WEBVTT

00:00:58.090 --> 00:01:00.903
Zapravo, ne idete često na zabave.

00:01:00.927 --> 00:01:04.744
(Smeh)

00:01:04.768 --> 00:01:05.935
Ako radite u prosveti,

00:01:05.959 --> 00:01:07.254
niste pozvani.

00:01:07.278 --> 00:01:10.317
(Smeh)

00:01:10.341 --> 00:01:14.360
I začudo nikad vas ne pozivaju ponovo,
to mi je veoma čudno.

00:01:14.384 --> 00:01:15.588
Ali ako odete na zabavu

00:01:15.612 --> 00:01:17.690
i neko vas pita: "Čime se bavite?"

00:01:17.714 --> 00:01:19.356
i odgovorite da radite u prosveti,

00:01:19.380 --> 00:01:21.224
vidite kako im lice prebledi.

00:01:21.248 --> 00:01:23.323
Sigurno misle: "O, bože, zašto baš ja?"

00:01:23.347 --> 00:01:26.076
(Smeh)

00:01:26.100 --> 00:01:27.847
"Moj jedini slobodan dan u nedelji."

00:01:27.871 --> 00:01:30.427
(Smeh)